{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"象她那样生","authors":["王守毅"],"dates":[{"year":1979,"month":6,"day":16}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"象她那样生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑龙江塔源林场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王守毅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"读完张志新的事迹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的心久久难平静——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脑海中出现了钢和铁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼前矗立起高山青松。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是何等闪光的思想和誓言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“要为真理而斗争！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活，象她那样生命火红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死，死得伟大而光荣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想起林彪、“四人帮”猖獗时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"神州大地万马喑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张志新啊，敢同魔鬼争高下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勇向黑暗夺光明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她是一面澄清的明镜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"显示着我们的灵魂和身影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她是一个光辉的楷模，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指示着我们眼前的人生……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}